Originally developed for use by tank commanders and helicopter pilots, NoiseAssassin 3.0 eliminates background noise better than any other headset. 

Music, video and calls never sounded better. With its 10mm wideband speaker—our biggest, most powerful speaker yet (25% larger than previous models)—podcasts, Pandora® tunes, YouTube® videos, driving directions and more come vibrantly to life in full-spectrum, HD-quality sound.

Jawbone ERA is the first headset with a built-in accelerometer and patented MotionX™ technology. Out of the box, you can ShakeShake® Jawbone ERA into pairing mode or TapTap® to answer phone calls.

You'll never run out of juice with Jawbone ERA. To check battery status, glance at the battery meter that automatically displays in the status bar of your iPhone® (Blackberry® and Android™ available at MyTALK).

Like other Jawbone products, Jawbone ERA gets better with time when synced with Jawbone's industry-first MyTALK platform. Download apps, customize new features like Caller ID by Name (exclusive to Jawbone ERA), set different voices or language options, even program Jawbone ERA to send emails and text messages using your voice.

AccessoryName: Jawbone JAMBOX BLACK bluetooth Speaker / Speaker phone
Descrip:
JAMBOX delivers stunning hi-fi audio in a portable wireless speaker so compact you won't believe it when you hear it. It's loud. With an output capacity of 85 decibels, JAMBOX fills even the largest rooms. Unlike other portable speakers, JAMBOX is powered by a pair of proprietary, highly sophisticated acoustic drivers, unmatched in their ability to produce extreme high (tweeter) and low (woofer) frequencies from a single, ultra-small dome speaker. They work in concert with an innovative moving-wall passive bass radiator and airtight enclosure to deliver shimmering highs and thumping lows that you can literally feel - the richest sound all in the palm of your hand.
 
JAMBOX is the only speaker in the world that gets smarter every time you plug it in. Just sync it with MyTALK, Jawbone's industry-first online platform to download apps, software upgrades, and the latest features - including LiveAudio™, an immersive three-dimensional listening experience. Jambox's integrated intelligence allows you to personalize it to your specific preferences. No other speaker on the planet is intelligent and updateable - but then again, nothing else is quite like JAMBOX.
 
With a powerful, built-in microphone, JAMBOX frees you to share crisp, clean-sounding conference calls anywhere - in the office, car, at home, alone or with a group. No more garbled, hard-to-hear chatter through your mobile phone or computer, no more being tied down by phone lines. Just crisp, clean wireless conference calls from your phone or computer. It's also perfect for sharing video chats via iChat®, Skype®, Google Talk™ and more. 
 
Don't let tiny computer speakers sap your sound. All your media deserves great audio, no matter what device it's played from. With JAMBOX, you'll feel the thump of every kick drum, the vroom of every car chase and crowd with every buzzer-beater - bringing all your mobile media vibrantly to life. And with about ten hours of continuous play, you can blast away all day long with plenty of charge to spare for whatever comes next.
DescripFR:
Jambox vous permet d'ecouter tous vos fichiers audio preferes-la musique, les balados, les videos, les applications, les jeux, et plus encore-a partir de tout telephone, lecteur mp3, tablette ou ordinateur portable
 
Vivez l'experience d'un son stereo enorme et d'une basse qui vous fera vibrer, le tout dans la paume de votre main
 
Apportez-le avec vous n'importe ou-d'une piece a une autre ou placez-le dans vorte sac et utilisez-le sur la route
 
Liberez-vous de l'encombrement des gros haut-parleurs dedies et les contraintes des cables et des stations d'accueil-la portabilite sans fil de JAMBOX satisfait a tous vos besoins d'ecoute dans un seul petit emballage
 
Partagez des appels sur la route en utilisant JAMBOX comme telephone haut parleur portable

Descrip:
Jawbone® ICON HD™ is equipped with the world's most advanced noise cancellation technology, military-grade NoiseAssassin® 2.5 with wind reduction. Originally developed for use by tank commanders and helicopter pilots, NoiseAssassin is a proprietary technology that eliminates unwanted background noise when you talk on the phone. It gives you the freedom to enjoy quiet phone conversations wherever you are. Whether you're at a noisy airport or on the road, your speech will sound crystal clear.

Music, video and calls never sounded better. With its large 10mm wideband speaker — our biggest, most powerful speaker yet (25% larger than ICON) — Jawbone ICON HD lets you privately listen to music, podcasts, YouTube® videos, sports, phone calls and more in full-spectrum, HD-quality sound. It's the most convenient way to enjoy all your mobile media and calls in one place.
 
Simultaneous Multipoint gives you the flexibility to manage audio and calls from two different phones or Bluetooth® devices at the same time. With the press of a button on your ICON HD, you can switch between calls on your personal and work phones.
 
You'll never run out of juice with Jawbone ICON HD. Just glance at the battery meter that automatically displays in the status bar of your iPhone® (BlackBerry® and Android™ available at MyTALK). Or, if your phone is out of reach, press the TALK button on ICON HD to hear an update: "About 5 hours of talk time remaining". 
 
Like other Jawbone products, ICON HD gets better with time when synced with Jawbone's industry-first MyTALK platform. Download apps, customize settings, hear calendar alerts and more. Jawbone Companion for Android will even dial you into conference calls at the press of a button — password and all! Just sign into mytalk.jawbone.com, plug in your headset, and sync whatever apps and updates you want. Make it yours at MyTALK.

Descrip:
When you want the look and feel of a hard case and the protection of a soft case... choose the sweet third option: CandyShell! It combines both hard shell and soft rubbery protection in a one-piece flexible iPhone 4S case.
The sleek, hard outer shell protects against impacts, plus slips easily in and out of your pockets. The rubbery lining absorbs shock and also extends to a bezel, which protects your screen if it falls screen-first, and gives it no-slip stability when you place it face down. The two-layered protection also makes for some sweet two-toned color options. One of Speck’s favorite cases for iPhone 4S!
DescripFR: Quand vous voulez que le regard et se sent d'un cas dur et la protection d'un cas doux... choisit la troisième option douce : CandyShell ! Il les deux combine écale fort et la protection caoutchouteuse douce dans un un-morceau iPhone flexible 4S cas. La coquille extérieure, dure et lustrée protège contre les impacts, plus les erreurs facilement en et de vos poches. Le revêtement caoutchouteux absorbe le choc et s'étend aussi à un panneau, qui protège votre écran s'il tombe écran-premier, et lui donne la stabilité d'aucun-erreur quand vous placez le fait face à en bas. La protection deux-disposé en couches fait aussi pour quelques options de couleur de deux-tonifié douces. Un de cas préférés de petite tache pour iPhone 4S !

Descrip: Our popular two-layer CandyShell is now available as a smooth-as-silk Satin case for iPhone 4S. Speck's smooth-as-silk CandyShell SATIN features two layers of iPhone 4S protection in a one-piece patent-pending design. It's got a hard outer shell to protect against impacts, plus a soft, rubbery inner layer and button covers to provide shock absorption. A raised bezel covers the edges and protects your screen if it falls face down. And the matte soft-touch coating gives you a great, grippy feel while preventing scuffs and scratches.
DescripFR: Notre CandyShell populaire de deux-couche est maintenant disponible aussi un lisse-que-la soie cas Satiné pour iPhone 4S. Petite tache lisse-comme-la soie CandyShell le SATIN présente deux couches d'iPhone 4S protection dans un un-morceau une conception brevet en attente. Il a obtenu une coquille extérieure dure pour protéger contre les impacts, plus un plus couche et plus les couvertures de bouton intérieurs caoutchouteux doux pour fournir l'absorption de choc. Un panneau haussé couvre les bords et protège votre écran s'il tombe le visage en bas. Et le revêtement de doux-touche de matte vous donne un grand, grippy se sent pendant qu'empêcher érafle et gratte.

AccessoryName: Speck iPhone4/4S Pixel Skin HD - Cobalt
AccessoryNameFR: Speck iPhone4/4S Pixel Skin HD - Cobalt
Descrip:
You don’t have to sacrifice protection and grippiness to use a slim iPhone case! PixelSkin HD is a thin, lightweight case that’s also protective, durable and abrasion resistant. It’s pliable and flexible, but not soft or sticky, so it slides easily in and out of your pockets. The touch-thru button covers are protective and satisfyingly press-able, right thru the case.
A raised screen bezel protects your iPhone even if it falls screen-first. The cool “pixel” texture gives you a little more grip on your phone, and creates a subtle yet eye-catching shiny/matte pattern.
DescripFR: Vous ne devez pas sacrifier la protection et grippiness pour utiliser un cas d'iPhone mince ! PixelSkin HD est un cas mince et léger qui est aussi protectif, durable et le frottement résistant. C'est flexible et flexible, mais pas doux ou collant, donc il glisse facilement en et de vos poches. Les couvertures de bouton de touche-à sont protectives et satisfaisamment de presse-capables, justes au cas. Un panneau haussé d'écran protège votre iPhone même s'il tombe écran-premier. La texture fraîche de « pixel » vous donne un peu plus de poigne sur votre téléphone, et crée un modèle de brillant/matte subtil et néanmoins attrayant.

• Sleek, elegant, and stylish

DescripFR:
Spécialement conçue pour votre téléphone intelligent BlackBerryMD, la pochette en cuir BlackBerryMD  préserve l'aspect et la beauté de votre téléphone.

Q'elle soit dans votre sac à main ou serviette, la pochette comprend une doublure lisse et douce pour protéger votre téléphone intelligent contre les chocs et les égratignures. 

De plus, l'étui comporte une technologie intuitive qui économise l'alimentation de la pile et reconnaît aussi vos paramètres et préférences de notification à l'intérieur de l'étui.

AccessoryNameFR: Étui Pivotant en Cuir pour Blackberry 9790 Noir
Descrip:
No matter how much you love your new BlackBerry® smartphone, sooner or later you're going to have to put it away. And there's no more convenient or better-looking place to put it than inside a BlackBerry® Leather Swivel Holster. The BlackBerry Leather Swivel Holsters are outfitted with a swivel clip to adjust the holster for maximum wearing comfort. What's more, the case includes intuitive technology that helps preserve battery power, while also recognizing your in-holster notification settings and preferences.

• BlackBerry® carrying cases are specifically engineered to fit and function appropriately with Blackberry® smartphones, and finished in a clean and stylish design that is the BlackBerry signature.
 
• Cases are tested for quality, durability, reliability and for optimal functionality, while ensuring compliance with specified tolerances and standards.
 
• The case includes technology that helps preserve battery power and works with BlackBerry smartphones so users can set in-holster notification settings and preferences (alerts, tones, volume levels) for phone, email and other applications.
 
• Authentic BlackBerry® Accessories – custom fit to your smartphone, robust design, and quality tested.
DescripFR:
Transportez votre téléphone intelligent BlackBerry en toute élégance dans cet étui pivotant.  

Votre téléphone BlackBerry va de pair avec cet étui spécialement conçu pour maximiser la durée de vie de la pile, pour ne pas manquer de messages et pour permettre aux utilisateurs de régler les paramètres du profil sans retirer le téléphone de l'étui.

 

·         L'extérieur en cuir durable protège le téléphone et doublure intérieure soyeuse protège et nettoie l'écran.

·         Le capteur de proximité magnétique indique au BlackBerry que vous l'avez mis de côté et qu'il n'est plus utilisé; le BlackBerry ferme alors l'écran et prolonge l'autonomie de votre pile.

Descrip:
Perfect for handwriting notes, natural sketches, and even recording audio clips, the HTC Scribe Digital Pen lets you transform the way you interact with your HTC Tablet

Pen-shaped design provides more natural and accurate interaction
Modern touchscreens are more responsive than ever before, but with a capacitive screen sometimes you miss out on the accuracy offered by using a stylus. With the HTC Tablet, this is a thing of the past. The HTC Scribe digital pen is comfortable to hold, and lets you write on your screen just as you would a piece of paper. So whether you're adding hand-written notes to a web page or quickly typing out an e-mail, with the HTC Tablet it's easier than ever before.

Can be used in a variety of apps for increased functionality
The HTC Scribe digital pen can be used for drawing, painting, writing, retouching photos, and even highlighting passages in the e-book application. Whatever you're doing, you can be sure of getting the most out of your HTC Tablet by using the Scribe digital pen. In the browser, you can make notes directly onto web pages. In the e-book app, any passages you highlight will be collated when you've finished, so you don't have to flick back through hundreds of pages to find that one stand-out quotation. 

Works as a voice recorder for linking audio to visual media
Another stand-out feature of the HTC Scribe digital pen is the ability to use it to record audio, and then transfer and link that to the visual media you've created. Whether it's adding notes to a presentation, or a voiceover to a storybook, you can bring your creations to life with the HTC Tablet and the Scribe digital pen. Please note, this functionality requires 1 x AAAA battery (included).
DescripFR:
Commentez des photos, écrivez et faites des captures d'écran de vos sites Web favoris avant de les partager sur vos réseaux sociaux!

Grâce à sa précision, le stylet magique HTC ScribeMC vous permettra de dessiner ou de prendre des notes facilement.

Stylet double fonction alimenté par pile pour améliorer votre précision pour écrire, éditer et dessiner sur votre HTC Tablet.

Le stylet est pourvu de deux boutons pour effacer et surligner votre le texte.
ApprovedComment: I have upc 821793012786.  I have cost as $40. - A.T. Dec 15th, 2011

AccessoryNameFR: Etui  d'Incipio pour Samsung Galaxy Nexus Noir
Descrip:
Measuring approximately 1.5mm in thickness, the feather® for Samsung Galaxy Nexus is a slim, form-fitting case that offers low-profile protection.  You will appreciate the sleek look of the feather® without adding excess bulk to your device. Obtain protection at its finest with the light-weight feather®.
 
With full access to all ports and buttons, the feather® provides superior protection while maintaining fully functional. The elevated buttons were strategically designed to make using your device easily accessible. Your Galaxy Nexus will remain protected while staying in-style.

  • Slim polycarbonate shell maintains form and functionality while protecting your smartphone from dents and scratches.
  • Soft touch matte finish easily slips into your pocket.
  • Convenient access to all ports and buttons, and large cut-outs allow easy access to volume controls.

·      Le logo gravé Incipio se mélange parfaitement avec le fini mat de cet étui.

Descrip:
The URBAN style Glider Gloves are low profile, light weight and slim fitting.

- Plaited inner lining and soft brushed interior layers for thermal insulation and protection.

Regular gloves simply do not work on touch screens - Glider Gloves do!
A Canadian company - Trust us, we know cold!

AccessoryNameFR: Carte mémoire microSDHC de 32 GB avec adaptateur
Descrip:
SanDisk introduces microSDHC (microSD) cards, launching this popular format into the high-capacity range of memory cards for mobile phones to provide more storage for music, videos, and quality photographs.
 
The microSDHC cards are only compatible in SDHC-supported devices designed to accommodate high-capacity cards.
 
For mobile phones that support microSD or TransFlash slots, the microSD module provides ample storage for use of media rich files such as music, videos, and photographs on the phone.
DescripFR:
SanDisk présente ses cartes microSDHC (microSD) et lance ce format très populaire dans la gamme haute capacité des cartes mémoire de téléphones cellulaires, qui offrent plus d'espace de stockage pour la musique, les vidéos et les photos de qualité.
 
Les cartes microSDHC sont compatibles uniquement avec les appareils SDHC conçus pour accueillir les cartes haute capacité.
 
D'une taille correspondant à environ un quart de celle d'une carte SD standard, la carte MicroSD offre une haute performance et une capacité de mémoire supérieure pour les téléphones dotés d'un emplacement pour carte TransFlash de SanDisk ou tout autre dispositif doté d'un emplacement pour carte MicroSD.
